{"id":107473,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":8,"day":16}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"妇友","column":"护士与助产士","genre":"","count":"280","ytitle":"","mtitle":"乡愁","ftitle":"","authors":["苏抒"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏抒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在逃亡里成长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流浪中茁壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去母爱的孩子呵!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝够了炎凉与辛酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐过牢狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遭过流放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年一一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是容易熬受的时间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜凉频来入梦，繁绕着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长白山灿烂的冰雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松花江的歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人，邻里，野地里的牛羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他(它)们依然健壮么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该不会给敌人的刺刀背"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揍折了腰吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八一五，永恒的八一五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它带来如焚的渴望!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怀念，负隅在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山沟子的人该站起来了吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸上俘获的战马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰向家园，越过荒坟野塚间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将光复的消息……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是慢着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽火掀天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪尖，刀尖是自己人的呢!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"够了，别再道出大篇理由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别再允许这样那样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道一一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生于斯，死于斯，祖宗坟莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉和土地都化在一起的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能主宰自己的命运么?"}]}